g>Challenging Storylines</strong></h2>New version enriches the plot story again. In order to save her hometown,Yimi invite the brave to start the Magic Card journey again.Hundreds of different plot levels and nightmare difficulty maps are waiting for you to breakthrough.There are more hidden levels waiting for you to discover!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391310/extras/a10bcd07d0683713c503a1cd7e787b41.poster.avif?t=1683798621\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391310/extras/a10bcd07d0683713c503a1cd7e787b41.webm?t=1683798621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391310/extras/a10bcd07d0683713c503a1cd7e787b41.mp4?t=1683798621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feature-packed Game</strong></h2>Game has rich and complete PVE functions,novel and ingenious design,roguelike creative gameplay,waiting for you to challenge!From Theives to Raider,Mystery Tower to Misterioso,Maze to Star Expedition,Dungeon to Elemental Tower,Infinity Palace to Wave of Evils,show your stronge deck to fight.Also,Season maps waiting for you to challenge!Great Rewards waiting for you to get!<br><br>Now come to experience pure classic card battles!Authentic strategic battles are waiting for you!",
